title: Trinity 037 (2009) (GreenGiant-DCP)
description:
Title: Trinity #37
Date: February 11, 2009

The war to save all of reality rages on and is waged in the memory of Superman, Batman and Wonder Woman. But the legendary Trinity battle to end the conflict themselves by becoming more than just a memory!

Written by Kurt Busiek and Fabian Nicieza
Art by Mark Bagley and Art Thibert, Scott McDaniel and Andy Owens, Tom Derenick and Wayne Faucher and Mike Norton and Ande Parks
Covers by Andy Kubert and Jesse Delperdang
